## Exit criteria

1. `compute_divergence.py --no-equal-n` accepted and documented.
2. `tab_div_biased_{method}.csv` produced for ≥4 representative methods.
3. `fig_zoo_bias_{method}.png` exists and renders for those methods.
4. `overview.md` contains bias theory with citations to Gretton and Pérez-Cruz.
5. Test above passes green.
